                <div class="col-xs-12">
                    <p>American Consumer Credit Counseling (ACCC) is a leading source for personalized <a href="/debt-management-advice">debt management advice</a> and programs to <a href="/consolidate-your-debt">consolidate your debt</a>. If you are interested in <a href="/consolidating-debts">consolidating debts</a>, contact one of ACCC's <a href="/credit-advisors">credit advisors</a> to learn how to <a href="/consolidate-bills">consolidate bills</a> without having to take a <a href="/consolidation-loan">consolidation loan</a> as would be suggested by some other <a href="/debt-relief-agencies">debt relief agencies</a>. As a Better Business Bureau <a href="/accredited-credit-counseling">accredited credit counseling</a> agency, you can count on ACCC for fair and honest <a href="/help-with-credit">help with credit</a> issues. We are also approved by the Department of Justice to provide pre-bankruptcy counseling and post-bankruptcy <a href="/credit-counseling-courses">credit counseling courses</a>.</p>
